# 🔔 Notification Types

Players receive notifications for:

- Friend Request
- Best Friend Request
- Party Invite
- Trade Request
- Gift Received
- Chat Message
- Buddy Message
- Achievement Unlocked
- Daily Reward Ready
- Event Started
- Event Ending Soon
- Index Reward Ready
- Marketplace Sale
- Keyboard Marketplace Download
- Profile Like
- Profile Comment

Blocked users cannot send notifications.

---

# ⚙ Notification Settings

Players can individually enable or disable:

- Friend Notifications
- Trade Notifications
- Gift Notifications
- Chat Notifications
- Event Notifications
- Achievement Notifications
- Marketplace Notifications
- Profile Notifications
- Sound
- Pop-up Animation

Buddy Mail is always enabled.

---

# 📩 Mail Features

Every mail supports:

- Read
- Unread
- Mark All Read
- Delete
- Favourite / Star
- Search
- Filters
- Categories
- Pin Mail

---

# 🎁 Gift Mail

Gift mails include:

- Accept
- Reject
- Claim Later

Claimed gifts remain in mail history.

---

# 📎 Mail Attachments

Mail attachments may contain:

- Coins
- XP
- Buddy XP
- Items
- Titles
- Frames
- Themes
- Badges

All rewards use a Claim button.

---

# 📜 Mail History

All mails remain permanently.

Players may:

- Delete mails manually
- View deleted mail history
- See claim status
- See read date
- See received date

Deleted reward mails cannot be claimed again.

---

# 📌 Favourite Mail

Players can mark important mails as Favourite.

Favourite mails always appear at the top.

Examples:

- First Achievement
- Founder Mail
- Rare Event Reward
- Birthday Letter

---

# 📊 Mail Statistics

Players can view:

- Total Mails Received
- Total Buddy Letters
- Total Gifts Claimed
- Total Event Mails
- Total Favourite Mails
- Total Deleted Mails

---

# 🔔 Bell Notification System

Whenever a new mail arrives:

- Bell icon gets a red notification dot
- Bell rings briefly
- Small notification appears

---

# 📬 Buddy House Mailbox

Buddy House contains a real Mailbox.

When new mail arrives:

- Mailbox shakes
- Red notification appears
- Buddy says:

> "Shubh! Tumhare liye nayi mail aayi hai!"

Players open the mailbox to read mails.

---

# 🎨 Mail Themes

Players can customize the mailbox interface.

Available themes:

- Classic
- Dark
- Halloween
- Christmas
- Valentine
- Neon

More seasonal themes will be added in future updates.

---

# 🔒 Privacy

Players control which notifications they receive.

Friend Requests follow privacy settings:

- Everyone
- Friends Only
- Nobody

Blocked players cannot interact.

---

# 🤖 Buddy Integration

Buddy participates throughout the system.

Buddy can:

- Celebrate rewards
- Send surprise letters
- Remind players about events
- Wish birthdays
- Congratulate achievements
- Notify about daily rewards

---

# Long-Term Goal

The Mail & Notification System will become the primary communication center of Roblox Buddy AI, permanently storing player history while connecting Friends, Trading, Economy, Achievements, Buddy, Buddy House, Inventory, Index, Events, Marketplace, and all future multiplayer systems into one seamless experience.